(ns farsund.theme.core
  (:require [mui.core :as mui]
            [mui.colors :as colors]
            [cuerdas.core :as str]
            [farsund.utils.core :as u]))


(def default-theme
  (-> (mui/create-mui-theme {:palette    {:primary   colors/blue-js
                                          :secondary colors/red-js
                                          ;:type      :dark
                                          }
                             :typography {:useNextVariants true}})
      (js->clj :keywordize-keys true)
      (u/transform-keys str/keyword)))
